title: @Riot: what is tahm kenchy boi's real name?
body:
Its said in tips while loading, "tahm kench was the name of the gambler that took his bargain"
or something along those lines.

like his demon fellow, {{champion:28}} they are referenced by their champion name.

So are demons nameless? or are only some of them named?

replies.body: Demons don't have names they just steal ones they like.
Tahm could really be, Fat Albert, Homer Simpson, Peter Griffin. Any fat television guy.

Demons are nameless as far as I know.

They don't really have "parents" so who the hell should give them their names?
